ZH: 我们是一个非常和睦的大家庭。
EN: We are a very harmonious big family.

ZH: 在这个大家庭里，每个人都有自己的责任。
EN: In this big family, everyone has their own responsibilities.

ZH: 大家庭里的兄弟姐妹们都很亲近。
EN: The brothers and sisters in the big family are very close.

ZH: 我们的大家庭总是充满欢笑和温暖。
EN: Our big family is always filled with laughter and warmth.

ZH: 大家庭里的长辈们对我们很关心。
EN: The elders in the big family care a lot about us.

ZH: 大家庭里的小孩子们总是闹闹哄哄的。
EN: The children in the big family are always lively and noisy.

ZH: 在大家庭里度过的每一个节日都让人难忘。
EN: Every holiday spent in the big family is unforgettable.

ZH: 大家庭里几乎每个人都会做菜。
EN: Almost everyone in the big family knows how to cook.

ZH: 大家庭里的气氛总是充满喜悦和团聚。
EN: The atmosphere in the big family is always full of joy and reunion.

ZH: 大家庭里的孩子们总是一起玩耍。
EN: The children in the big family always play together.

ZH: 在大家庭里，大家共同面对生活的挑战。
EN: In the big family, everyone faces life's challenges together.

ZH: 大家庭里传承着许许多多的家族传统。
EN: The big family carries on many family traditions.

ZH: 在这个大家庭里，我们的爱永远不会变。
EN: In this big family, our love will never change.

ZH: 大家庭的每个成员都很重要。
EN: Every member of the big family is important.

ZH: 在大家庭里，大家都有自己的职责。
EN: In the big family, everyone has their own duties.

ZH: 大家庭里的每个人都是家中的支柱。
EN: Everyone in the big family is a pillar of the household.

ZH: 大家庭的团结是我们的力量所在。
EN: The unity of the big family is our strength.

ZH: 大家庭里的每一颗心都是互相连接的。
EN: Every heart in the big family is connected to each other.

ZH: 大家庭里的每一次聚会都是一次盛大的庆典。
EN: Every gathering in the big family is a grand celebration.

ZH: 大家庭的温暖和爱意包围着我们。
EN: The warmth and love of the big family surround us.
